<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.8">
<l>kaṟṟiṉa mēykkavum mēykkappeṟṟāṉ kāṭuvāḻ cātiyu mākappeṟṟāṉ</l>
<l>paṟṟi yuraliṭai yāppumuṇṭāṉ pāvikā ḷuṅkaḷuk kēccukkolō</l>
<l>kaṟṟaṉa pēci vacaiyuṇātē kālika ḷuyya maḻaitaṭuttuk</l>
<l>koṟṟak kuṭaiyāka vēntiniṉṟa kōvart taṉatteṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘He got to feed the herds of calves as [He] grazed [them]; He got to be of a birth</l>
<l rend="indent">that lives in the forest;</l>
<l>He got tied up to the mortar [being] caught!’ Wretches! Is [this] reproachable for you?</l>
<l>Do not get scolded [by me] speaking what you have learned!</l>
<l>Send me to Govardana where [He] stood holding up [the hill] as a victorious umbrella,</l>
<l rend="indent">Blocking the rains so that the herds of cows are saved.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
